snippet.title: Hooklings Trailer
snippet.description:
Hook, pull, jump and do combos to clear 100 screens of enemies, alone or with your friends in this platformer inspired by arcade classics from the 80s.

Buy it on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1018240/Hooklings/

Buy it on itch.io
https://pasculator.itch.io/hooklings

Subscribe for more videos of indie game development.
